新益智游戏“Strands”将加入《纽约时报》的“Wordle”和“Connections”行列https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-puzzle-game-strands-to-join-wordle-and-connections-at-the-new-york-times-3596929?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=新的益智游戏链在纽约时报加入单词和连接Ryan EasbyTue, 05 Mar 2024 14:07:47 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3596929 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="字词答案" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是《纽约时报》推出的第三款游戏</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-puzzle-game-strands-to-join-wordle-and-connections-at-the-new-york-times-3596929">纽约时报的新益智游戏“Strands”与“Wordle”和“Connections”一起</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="字词答案" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Wordle-answer-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一款新的益智游戏<em>Strands</em>与<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/wordle">Wordle</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/connections"><em>Connections</em></a>一起被添加到<em>《纽约时报》</em>文字游戏阵容中。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-review-3590691">《最终幻想 7 重生》评论：这部一流的重制版将带你进入云九</a></strong></li></ul><p>游戏的目标是找到所有有共同点的单词，以及描述每个单词有共同点并触及棋盘两侧的“spangram”。玩家能够垂直、水平和对角连接字母，并且能够在单词中间切换方向，从而提供更多样的潜在解决方案。</p><p> “我在查看比赛时发现，没有那么多带有扭曲的单词搜索。除了寻找语言之外，我们如何让成年人感到有趣？” <em>《纽约时报》</em>游戏团队研究总监朱丽叶特·塞伊在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/03/04/crosswords/strands-word-search-game.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时表示。</p><p> “我希望像我的搭档和他奶奶这样怀念单词搜索的人能够在这款游戏中找到归宿。” </p><figure id="attachment_3518329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3518329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3518329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wordle-credit-Jonathan-RaaNurPhoto-via-Getty@2000x1270.jpg" alt="沃德尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wordle-credit-Jonathan-RaaNurPhoto-via-Getty@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wordle-credit-Jonathan-RaaNurPhoto-via-Getty@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wordle-credit-Jonathan-RaaNurPhoto-via-Getty@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wordle-credit-Jonathan-RaaNurPhoto-via-Getty@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wordle-credit-Jonathan-RaaNurPhoto-via-Getty@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wordle-credit-Jonathan-RaaNurPhoto-via-Getty@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3518329" class="wp-caption-text">字。图片来源：Jonathan Raa/NurPhoto 来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “spangram 应该以某种方式总结事情。它几乎就像一个交叉世界中的揭示者，它向你展示是什么连接了所有这些单词，” <em>Wordle</em>和<em>Strands</em>编辑特雷西·贝内特 (Tracy Bennett) 在同一次采访中解释道。</p><p>这个想法是在<em>《纽约时报》</em>所说的年度游戏盛会期间提出的，每个人都在会上推出了一款他们希望看到的游戏加入到该网站提供的游戏精选中。目前，三个可用的游戏是<em>Wordle、Connections</em>和<em>Strands</em>本身。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch">任天堂 Switch</a>模拟器 Yuzu 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nintendo">任天堂</a>提起诉讼后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-switch-emulator-yuzu-shuts-down-must-pay-1-9million-3596876">被迫关闭</a>。除了关闭他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-3ds">任天堂 3DS</a>模拟器 Citra 之外，该模拟器的开发商还必须支付 190 万英镑的赔偿金。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-puzzle-game-strands-to-join-wordle-and-connections-at-the-new-york-times-3596929">纽约时报的新益智游戏“Strands”与“Wordle”和“Connections”一起</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
